OL,5,CHAVE YOURSELF A GREEN CHRISTMAS  Q l|$ 
OL,7, If you're a faithful follower of all   
OL,8, things eco-friendly - Christmas is not 
OL,9, the time when you should beCputting    
OL,10,Cyour feet up!                          
OL,12, So alertsCNeil VerlanderGfromCFriends  
OL,13,Cof the Earth.G"If you've been a hard-  
OL,14, working eco-warrior all year, don't    
OL,15, spoil things by letting go now.        
OL,17, "SureCtake it easy, pig outG- indulge  
OL,18, in the season's cheer but make sure you
OL,19, have yourself a green Christmas!"      
