OL,4,B`````````````````````````````````R.?$
OL,5,CHAVE YOURSELF A GREEN CHRISTMAS  Q l|$ 
OL,7, Are you the kind of Christmas shopper  
OL,8, who has left it till now to get        
OL,9,CChristmas cards?GFear not, says Neil   
OL,10, Verlander from Friends of the Earth.   
OL,12,C"ReuseGyour cards from last year or    
OL,13, else make your own from recycled       
OL,14, materials.                             
OL,16, "If you're wrapping pressies, buy      
OL,17,Crecycled paperGand wrap them carefully 
OL,18, so that the wrapper can be reused or   
OL,19, else use old fabric to wrap."          
