OL,4,B`````````````````````````````````R.?$
OL,5,CHAVE YOURSELF A GREEN CHRISTMAS  Q l|$ 
OL,7, "Once the season of goodwill is over,  
OL,8, the UK alone is expected toCdump a mega
OL,9,C700 million cards,Gdon't add your lot  
OL,10, to them," says Neil Verlander from     
OL,11, Friends of the Earth.                  
OL,13, "TheCPost OfficeGis joining forces     
OL,14, with theCCountryside CommissionGto run 
OL,15, a Christmas card recycling scheme.     
OL,17,C"Between December 29 and January 31,   
OL,18, drop off all your old Christmas cards  
OL,19, at your local post office."            
