OL,4,B`````````````````````````````````R.?$
OL,5,CHAVE YOURSELF A GREEN CHRISTMAS  Q l|$ 
OL,7, Just ten per cent of old Christmas     
OL,8, cards are currently recycled, the vast 
OL,9, majorityCend up as landfill each year. 
OL,11, Money raised by the Post Office scheme 
OL,12, will go to 11 Community Forests in     
OL,13, England toCsupport tree planting       
OL,14,Cschemes.                               
OL,16, Last year, the scheme resulted in      
OL,17,C#23,500Gof Christmas cards being       
OL,18, recycled, which paid for the planting  
OL,19, ofC11,000 trees.                       
