OL,4,B`````````````````````````````````R.?$
OL,5,CHAVE YOURSELF A GREEN CHRISTMAS  Q l|$ 
OL,7, "Most of theCChristmas treesGsold in   
OL,8, this country are grown in nurseries,"  
OL,9, says Neil Verlander from Friends of the
OL,10, Earth. "When you've finished with your 
OL,11, one, you don't have to throw it away.  
OL,13, "You couldCplant itGoutside. Bearing   
OL,14, this in mind, make sure that while it's
OL,15, indoors it's kept in a cool place.     
OL,17, "Or else, contact your local council   
OL,18, aboutCgreen waste shredding facilities,
OL,19, this ensures there's no waste."        
