OL,5,CHAVE YOURSELF A GREEN CHRISTMAS  Q l|$ 
OL,7, "As soon as Christmas is over, aside   
OL,8, from finding yourself a couple of      
OL,9, pounds heavier in weight, you'll also  
OL,10, find you've gotCloads of rubbish,"Gsays
OL,11, expert Neil Verlander.                 
OL,13, "No-one can escape the season's mound  
OL,14, ofCwaste glass and paper.GMake sure    
OL,15, that any paper you don't re-use gets   
OL,16, recycled along with empty bottles.     
OL,18, "For information aboutCrecycling       
OL,19,Cschemes and depots call your council." 
