OL,5,CHAVE YOURSELF A GREEN CHRISTMAS  Q l|$ 
OL,7, If you're buyingCChristmas presentsG   
OL,8, over the next few days, Friends of the 
OL,9, Earth's Neil Verlander advises you to: 
OL,11,BGAvoid excessCpackaging and wrapping. 
OL,12,BGBefore buying aCwooden giftGfind out 
OL,13,   where it's from. Buy second-hand,    
OL,14,   reclaimed or sustainable wood gifts. 
OL,15,BCTake your own bagsGto bring Christmas
OL,16,   shopping home in.                    
OL,18, "Consider your green Christmas efforts 
OL,19,Ca gift to the planet.GHave a good one!"
